item.title: GEDbpedia - online global encyclopedic database
item.description: GEDbpedia - is an online free encyclopedia database (similar to IMDb and Wikipedia), that provides facts and articles with pictures, videos, and images. And can offer information about celebrities and people, books, movies and television shows, and much more.

item.title: Merman Academy: The Movie (2020 film) - GEDbpedia
item.description: Merman Academy: The Movie is a 2020 American comedy/fantasy/family film written, directed, produced, and edited by Zeke Taylor and Jabari Leggette. It stars Zeke Taylor, Immoney Cooper, Jabari Leggette, Earnest Harper, and Malachi Taylor, and is narrated by Zeke Taylor. Merman Academy: The Movie was globally released on June 24th, 2020 by Balckflix Productions.

item.title: Zeke Taylor (American actor and internet personality) - GEDbpedia
item.description: Zeke Taylor (born December 29, 2005) is an American actor and internet personality from Arkansas.
